msgctxt "5856"
msgid "Yasuko"
msgstr "Yasuko"

msgctxt "84_Date"
msgid "Hold on a sec, Kiryu."
msgstr "Hold on a sec, Kiryu."

msgctxt "96_Kiryu"
msgid "What's wrong?"
msgstr "¿Qué ocurre?"

msgctxt "108_Date"
msgid "There's something I need to tell you."
msgstr "There's something I need to tell you."

msgctxt "120_Date"
msgid "Couldn't really say it in there."
msgstr "Couldn't really say it in there."

msgctxt "132_Kiryu"
msgid "Does it involve Yasuko-san?"
msgstr "Does it involve Yasuko-san?"

msgctxt "144_Date"
msgid "You bet. If she found out about this, she'd just end up\\r\n"\n"getting herself into more trouble."
msgstr "You bet. If she found out about this, she'd just end up\\r\n"\n"getting herself into more trouble."

msgctxt "156_Kiryu"
msgid "Well? What is it?"
msgstr "Well? What is it?"

msgctxt "168_Date"
msgid "Well... You only just got here so you probably haven't\\r\n"\n"noticed, but the whole town's been kinda on edge lately."
msgstr "Well... You only just got here so you probably haven't\\r\n"\n"noticed, but the whole town's been kinda on edge lately."

msgctxt "180_Kiryu"
msgid "Because of Saejima?"
msgstr "Because of Saejima?"

msgctxt "192_Date"
msgid "Partially, I'm sure. But there's more to it than that."
msgstr "Partially, I'm sure. But there's more to it than that."

msgctxt "204_Date"
msgid "Word on the street is, Majima and Saejima linked up a few\\r\n"\n"days ago."
msgstr "Word on the street is, Majima and Saejima linked up a few\\r\n"\n"days ago."

msgctxt "216_Kiryu"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

msgctxt "228_Date"
msgid "Yup. I hear Majima had his boys line the whole damn street\\r\n"\n"to keep the cops off Saejima."
msgstr "Yup. I hear Majima had his boys line the whole damn street\\r\n"\n"to keep the cops off Saejima."

msgctxt "240_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh. So they've already met."
msgstr "Huh. So they've already met."

msgctxt "252_Kiryu"
msgid "Speaking of, Date-san... do you know where I can find\\r\n"\n"Majima-san? I need to talk to him as soon as possible."
msgstr "Speaking of, Date-san... do you know where I can find\\r\n"\n"Majima-san? I need to talk to him as soon as possible."

msgctxt "264_Kiryu"
msgid "Not just about Saejima. Majima-san might be able to tell me\\r\n"\n"more about the connection between the top police brass,\\r\n"\n"Jingu, and the Tojo Clan."
msgstr "Not just about Saejima. Majima-san might be able to tell me\\r\n"\n"more about the connection between the top police brass,\\r\n"\n"Jingu, and the Tojo Clan."

msgctxt "276_Date"
msgid "The police? What are you talking about?"
msgstr "The police? What are you talking about?"

msgctxt "288_Kiryu"
msgid "Sorry, but I can't say much more than that. Just know that\\r\n"\n"people are gunning for the Tojo."
msgstr "Sorry, but I can't say much more than that. Just know that\\r\n"\n"people are gunning for the Tojo."

msgctxt "300_Kiryu"
msgid "And no matter what's going down, I need to hear Majima-san's\\r\n"\n"side of the story."
msgstr "And no matter what's going down, I need to hear Majima-san's\\r\n"\n"side of the story."

msgctxt "312_Date"
msgid "All right. Last I heard, he'd taken root up on the top floor\\r\n"\n"of the Millennium Tower. Starting there's your best bet."
msgstr "All right. Last I heard, he'd taken root up on the top floor\\r\n"\n"of the Millennium Tower. Starting there's your best bet."

msgctxt "324_Kiryu"
msgid "Great. Thanks, Date-san."
msgstr "Great. Thanks, Date-san."

msgctxt "396_Kiryu"
msgid "(Can't think of a better place to talk than New Serena.)"
msgstr "(Can't think of a better place to talk than New Serena.)"

msgctxt "408_Kiryu"
msgid "Yasuko-san, there's a bar near here that I used to go to\\r\n"\n"back in the day. We can catch our breath there for a bit."
msgstr "Yasuko-san, there's a bar near here that I used to go to\\r\n"\n"back in the day. We can catch our breath there for a bit."

msgctxt "420_Yasuko"
msgid "Okay, I'll follow your lead."
msgstr "Okay, I'll follow your lead."

